'''鈍獸屬'''（{{lang-xm|Barytherium}}）為[[長鼻目|長鼻目]][[鈍獸科|鈍獸科]]下已滅絕的一屬，生存於[[始新世|始新世]]晚期至[[漸新世|漸新世]]早期的北非。鈍獸為目前化石紀錄中最早出現的大型長鼻目物種，肩高{{convert|1.8|to|2.0|m}}，體重可達{{convert|2|t}}<ref name="probos_mass">{{Cite journal | last1 = Larramendi | first1 = A. | last2 =  | first2 =  | year = 2016 | title = Shoulder height, body mass and shape of proboscideans | journal = Acta Palaeontologica Polonica | volume = 61 | issue =  | pages =  | publisher =  | jstor =  | doi = 10.4202/app.00136.2014 | url = https://www.app.pan.pl/archive/published/app61/app001362014.pdf | accessdate =  | archive-date = 2016-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160824042509/http://www.app.pan.pl/archive/published/app61/app001362014.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
