[[File:Barytherium_molar.jpg|thumb]]
鈍獸屬的[[模式種|模式種]]為 ''Barytherium grave''，發現於20世紀初期的[[埃及|埃及]][[法尤姆|法尤姆]]<ref>Andrews, C.W. 1901. Über das Vorkommen von Proboscidiern in untertertiären Ablagerungen Aegyptens. ''Tageblatt des V Internationalen Zoologischen Kongresses, Berlin'' '''6''': 4–5.</ref>。在這之後，於[[利比亞|利比亞]]與[[阿曼|阿曼]]均有發現更為完整的鈍獸化石<ref>[http://main.omanobserver.om/node/51944 "Bones of Elephant Ancestors Found"] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110805044209/http://main.omanobserver.om/node/51944 |date=August 5, 2011 }}, ''The Omani Observer'', May 22, 2011, retrieved May 22, 2011.</ref>。鈍獸的外表與現存[[亞洲象|亞洲象]]相似，但是具有八根較短的獠牙，上下顎各四根，獠牙形式比起大象更像是現存的[[河馬|河馬]]。上顎獠牙為向下垂直生長，下顎獠牙則水平向外突出，推測可能可以用來切斷植物組織<ref name="MamEv">{{cite book |author= Savage, RJG |author2= Long, MR |last-author-amp= yes|year=1986 |title= Mammal Evolution: an illustrated guide|url= https://archive.org/details/mammalevolutioni0000sava  |publisher= Facts on File|location=New York|isbn= 0-8160-1194-X|page= [https://archive.org/details/mammalevolutioni0000sava/page/148 148]}}</ref>。

